{"tid":1299502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"語言偽術：議事規則根本無“壽終正寢”呢四個字，唔係我唔想信，係林奠信唔過","createTime":"2019-07-09T05:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T06:07:17.000Z","uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6a72773140b0dd5a22cddf78a98537ae51d6e80a","tid":1299502,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"佢死都唔肯切切實實講撤回，仲用左&ldquo;壽終正寢&rdquo;呢種比喻既字眼<br />\n背後好可能有其他計劃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CBRn0wd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCBRn0wd.png&h=b258b1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你同我搵下議事規則邊度有&ldquo;壽終正寢&rdquo;呢四個字啦屌你老母<br />\n正式用詞都咁亂黎？一定有d野<br />\n<br />\n同埋一日未救到義士，一日都未成功<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果林奠一早撤回，本來呢班人係唔駛俾人拉，可以安安樂樂係屋企<br />\n係仆街政府搞到佢地面臨被檢控既風險</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要政府承諾永遠不檢控義士</span>"},{"pid":"2cc9113bd98506f88958e7793fe427fa7dc5b8ea","tid":1299502,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2c3be3a2edbeb9a046fb0386022d12bae52afe4","tid":1299502,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}